  <TITLE>break  </TITLE>
  <TYPE>Scilab Function  </TYPE>
  <DATE>April 1993  </DATE>
  <SHORT_DESCRIPTION name="break"> interruption d&apos;une boucle  </SHORT_DESCRIPTION>
  <DESCRIPTION>
  <P>
    A l&apos;intérieur d&apos;une boucle <VERB>for</VERB> ou <VERB>while</VERB>, la commande <VERB>break</VERB> force la boucle à se terminer.
  </P>
  </DESCRIPTION>
  <EXAMPLE><![CDATA[
k=0; while 1==1, k=k+1; if k > 100 then  break,end; end
 ]]></EXAMPLE>
